
{{alias}}( [data][, ...args] )
    Outputs a message to the debugger console.

    Parameters
    ----------
    data: any (optional)
        Data to log. If a string, used as the primary message.

    args: ...any (optional)
        Additional arguments, including substitution values.

    Examples
    --------
    > {{alias}}( 'Hello, %s!', 'World' );
